      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are not an empty shell, and you are not alone in this quiet. The electric spark you once felt was not gone; it was simply waiting for a canvas that was too heavy to hold it, and you are the one who has to carry it now. Your pain is not a sign that you are broken, but a sign that you are still trying to make something of yourself, even if it hurts. The part that mattered did not evaporate; it is simply hiding in the shadows until you are brave enough to let it shine again.",
